{
  "stem": "27507.10",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And then there was my father, and I, and a whole family of a judge, Miller, of his daughter, and his mother, and his sister, I think.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "But the mother, the wife-- he was himself, I think he-- he was-- I'm not sure what happened to him.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "But his wife was outside, was not at Koper's.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And her family-- and her family of-- and the German Jew, Rolf Neuding, who was-- who didn't even speak Polish, because he was really German.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And he spoke only German.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And his girlfriend, and her sister, and the sister's son, so there were about, altogether 10, or 11, or 12 people in those two rooms.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And there was a lodger as well, who was called [POLISH], that means one who has luck, although his luck was doubtful.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "But he was a young chap, who was living from smuggling.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And he was-- they were all-- the point that I was trying to make was that they were all very simple people, not at all educated, highly educated, or-- really, pretty-- very, very simple.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And they saved us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "And nobody ever denounced us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "So it is all pretty amazing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "Not only that, but there were-- they didn't even-- Marta and Copper, they didn't keep so under completely under cover, because few times a year, there were family feasts.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "There was a birthday, his birthday, her birthday, anniversary, something like that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "And then they would invite even more family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "They would invite-- Marta's sister who would come, with her husband who was a drunkard, who was a perpetual drunkard.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "And his sister-- her sister was a market woman.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "She was selling in one of the Warsaw markets.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "And so they were there, and some other family.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "And everybody would get terribly drunk, terribly drunk on vodka.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
